summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Building and authorizing an offer for sale by competitive bidding procedures of a certain remainder property held for general corporate purposes, known as the Juanita Gravel Pit, and located in a portion of the Northeast Quarter of the Northwest Quarter of Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 5 East, W.M. (Arbitrary File address known as 10799 N.E. 132nd St., Kirkland, Washington).
